data.description: Beautiful home with an open floor plan with three bedrooms and two full bathrooms along with a spacious finished room above the garage. Home is in close proximity to the Coast Guard Base! This home includes a tankless hot water heater, granite counter tops in the kitchen, and whirlpool stainless steel appliances. Home is located on a spacious lot, with a beautiful backyard view.
